name: 6-phosphofructokinase
classes: Phosphotransferases with an alcohol group as acceptor
comment: D-Tagatose 6-phosphate and sedoheptulose 7-phosphate can act as acceptors. UTP, CTP and ITP can act as donors. Not identical with EC 2.7.1.105 6-phosphofructo-2-kinase.
